story.storykicker: The Uttar Pradesh Polytechnic JEECUP entrance examination results 2016 are likely to be declared today at www.jeecup.org
story.storybody:
The Uttar Pradesh Polytechnic JEECUP entrance examination results 2016 are expected to be declared today at www.jeecup.org by the Uttar Pradesh JEE council.

The entrance exam was conducted in the month of May by the Uttar Pradesh Polytechnic Sanyukt Pravesh Pariksha known as JEECUP at various centres across the state.

Steps to check the UP Polytechnic Entrance Results 2016:

  • Log on to the official website www.jeecup.org
  • Click on JEECUP 2016 results
  • Enter your roll number
  • Result will appear on the screen
  • Take a hard copy of it for future reference.

About Joint Entrance Examination Council (Sanyukt Pravesh Pariksha Parishad, U.P)

The Joint Entrance Examination Council was established on November 4, 1986 under the society act of 1860. The principal secretary of Technical and Vocational Education, Uttar Pradesh is the ex-officio chairman of the council.
